Test UDR/TEST002 fails with a weird Java error, indicating that there is some inconsistency in the loaded Java classes.
```
*** ERROR[11224] The Java virtual machine raised an exception. Details: java.lang.AbstractMethodError: org.TRAFODION.sql.udr.UDRInvocationInfo.setUDRWriterCompileTimeData(Lorg/TRAFODION/sql/udr/UDRWriterCompileTime
Data;)V
```
Class UDRInvocationInfo is not an abstract class and this method was not changed recently, so we must have some other inconsistency in the loaded Java classes.
